headline: Is Intuit’s AI Innovation a Signal to Reconsider Its Stock in 2025?
summary: Wondering whether Intuit stock is a good buy right now? You are not alone, especially with so much debate about how to value fast-growing software leaders like this. Even though Intuit’s share price dipped by 0.4% over the past week and is down 2.4% over the past year, the stock is still up an impressive 93.0% over the past five years and 65.3% in the last three.
